import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter, Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './pages/Home'

export default function Routess(){
    return(
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
                <Route exact path="/" element={<Home />}>
                    <Home/>
                </Route> 
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )

}
